Taking commissions for Roblox game/group logos
Prices vary from 100-250 depending on how much work is put into the logo. I am flexible with all fonts, the logo does not need to look like one of the logos below I can make it a different style. Taking payouts up front through group funds.
Logo can say whatever you want and have any colors you want, the logos in the picture are just the ways I like my logos. 
I have a few months working with GFX like this.
More details can be discussed in DM's. Thank you. :)
